Logical_source_description.0: Polar UVI Level-1 Full Resolution Imager Data

TEXT.1: CDAWeb displayed images have time-tags shifted 51 seconds back from nominal Epoch

TEXT.2: This corrects that H2 Epochs are telemetry times, not centered collection time

TEXT.3: 51 seconds is an approximate, typical correction.  Exact values depend on modes and transition status.

MODS.0: Initial work at SPDF 3/20-x/xx/2001 by REM

MODS.1: This dataset was renamed  from po_h2_uvi and po_l1_uvi to po_level1_uvi on 5/6/2005 in CDAWeb
